items.title: Military says it has seized power in Madagascar after president moves to 'safe place'
items.description: The military promises elections within two years, but President Rajoelina insists he is still in charge.

items.title: Israel identifies bodies of first four dead hostages returned by Hamas
items.description: The first four deceased hostages to be returned are Guy Illouz, Bipin Joshi, Yossi Sharabi and Daniel Peretz.

items.title: French pair sentenced in Iran on spying charges
items.description: The defendants are believed to be couple Cecile Kohler and Jacques Paris, who were arrested in 2022.
